
Skill type: offensive
Usage duration: random
Affecting stats: Str/Dex/Weapon
Affecting skills: Whirling slash, vital points, Crushing, Finishing move

Whirling slash is one of the most powerful offensive skills in the world of Deleria.
Warrior who knows how to use whirling slash is a very powerful opponent because
the expert using of weapons. Knowledge in skill vital points helps
warrior deal more damage. Crushing and finishing move sometimes can be combined
to the main slash if warrior is skilled enough.

Being in berserk will affect on damage also.
